data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value: Times are tough, the crime rate is up 200% and the prisons are full. We can't afford to incarcerate everyone convicted of a crime so the burden is place on you, our most experienced judge, to decide whether the convicted criminals are deserving of one of the very few open cells or if there is a chance for them to peacefully reside in society without time served. Know this, if you fail to produce tangible results you too will be on the next bus to a 8x4 cell. Good Luck!
